   7:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h **** /** A handle for interacting with an I2C peripheral. This is a dumb
   8:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *  gateway that internally points to one of the four I2C peripherals
   9:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *  after it was initialised. It can then be copied and passed around.
  10:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *  Use an I2CHandle like this:
  11:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *  
  12:../libdaisy_IIT6/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *      // setup the configuration
